cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech transcriptions and language processing to extract entity-video frame pairs.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper involves visual grounding tasks and image recognition.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper proposes a method for automatically constructing task-specific training sets.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with automated annotation and meta-algorithms.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with audio-visual data and video streaming services.
